snippet.title: ShowBiz Minute: Depp, Rowling, Starr
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp takes stand in libel trial, claims Amber Heard hit him; JK Rowling, Margaret Atwood and Gloria Steinem among 150 writers, activists and academics who have signed a letter giving a warning over free speech; Ringo Starr celebrates his 80th birthday quarantine-style. (July 8)
